      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">
            The average Canadian driver visits a service center 2-3 times per year. But here's the problem: most of those visits aren't happening at your shop. They're happening at quick lubes, dealership service departments, and your competitorsâ€”simply because those businesses stay top of mind while you don't.
          </p>

          <p>
            This guide will show you how to build systems that capture every possible service visit from your existing customers, bring in new customers consistently, and reduce the administrative burden that's burning out you and your team.
          </p>

          <!-- Table of Contents -->
