            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4 mt-0">What You'll Learn</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-0">
              <li><a href="#retention" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Why Customer Retention Is Everything</a></li>
              <li><a href="#service-reminders" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Building a Service Reminder System</a></li>
              <li><a href="#online-booking" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Implementing Online Booking</a></li>
              <li><a href="#declined-services" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Following Up on Declined Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="#reviews" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Building Your Online Reputation</a></li>
